      { q: "Is Belgium playing at home at the 2026 World Cup?", a: "Yes. The Hockey World Cup 2026 is co-hosted by Belgium (Wavre) and the Netherlands (Amstelveen). Belgium's Pool B matches are played at the Belfius Hockey Arena — essentially their home ground." }
